2003/09/25: Dek
	* SearchTab: reworked SearchSyntax
		Default is now: all words are AND'ed together. If you don't want this
			use  * "OR searchpattern" 
			or   * "ANDNOT searchpattern", which is the same as "-searchpattern"	
				
